OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,FAnnabelle, one of the students who
OL,7,Fcontracted meningitis, speaks to ITV
OL,8,FNews' Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,9,FBarry
OL,11,FA University of Kent student has told
OL,12,FITV News how she was left temporarily
OL,13,Fblind and unable to walk after
OL,14,Fcontracting meningitis.
OL,16,FAnnabelle Mackay had been out
OL,17,Fcelebrating her 21st birthday at Club
OL,18,FChemistry - the venue the Kent
OL,19,Foutbreak is thought to be connected to
OL,20,F- in early March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
