FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773921770
OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fconfirmed on Wednesday that there are
OL,8,F20 cases of meningitis being
OL,9,Finvestigated in Kent.
OL,11,FNine of those cases have been
OL,12,Fconfirmed, of which six are the
OL,13,Fmeningitis B strain, known as MenB.
OL,14,FTwo students have died after
OL,15,Fcontracting the bacterial infection.
OL,17,FAnnabelle, who is studying law, had
OL,18,Fgone to a different club on March 4,
OL,19,Fbefore heading to Club Chemistry the
OL,20,Fday after.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
