OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,FFive days later, Annabelle became
OL,7,Funwell - feeling delirious and
OL,8,Fseverely fatigued, drifting in and out
OL,9,Fof consciousness. She also developed a
OL,10,Ffever and a severe headache.
OL,12,F"I was really sensitive to light, and
OL,13,FI was also really sensitive to noise
OL,14,Fas well", she described.
OL,16,F"I had headphones on to kind of help
OL,17,Fwith the noise and I had a eye mask on
OL,18,Ffor the light, because I couldn't
OL,19,Fhandle any kind of light", Annabelle
OL,20,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773921770
OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,FBelieving it was Covid at first,
OL,7,FAnnabelle took a test which came back
OL,8,Fnegative. She asked her housemate to
OL,9,Fhelp her call 111, who advised rest
OL,10,Fand fluids.
OL,12,FHer housemates took her to Canterbury
OL,13,FMedical Centre, but as her symptoms
OL,14,Fcontinued to worsen, she was rushed in
OL,15,Fan ambulance to a resuscitation unit
OL,16,Fin Margate Hospital.
OL,18,F"I couldn't talk, I couldn't move, I
OL,19,Fcouldn't see", Annabelle said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
