CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773921770
OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,F"On Thursday, I woke up and I couldn't
OL,7,Fsee at all. I was in hospital but I
OL,8,Fthought I was still in my university
OL,9,Fhouse."
OL,11,FAnnabelle said that her heart goes out
OL,12,Fto the lives lost, adding that her
OL,13,Fexperience has "put a new perspective
OL,14,Fon life, 100%". Annabelle hopes to
OL,15,Fleave hospital on Wednesday.
OL,17,FShe told ITV News that she believes
OL,18,Fthere should be more education around
OL,19,Fmeningitis and its symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
