OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,F"A lot of (the information) is centred
OL,7,Faround a rash, but I didn't develop a
OL,8,Frash until quite late on, until I was
OL,9,Fin the Margate hospital", she said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FGPs across the country have now been
OL,17,Ftold to prescribe antibiotics to
OL,18,Fanyone who visited Club Chemistry in
OL,19,FCanterbury from March 5-7, plus
OL,20,Fstudents from the University of Kent.
