OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,FThis is to ensure anyone who has left
OL,7,Fcampus can make sure they get the
OL,8,Fright treatment.
OL,10,FSo far, more than 2,500 doses have
OL,11,Fbeen given to students, close contacts
OL,12,Fand others ` including some of those
OL,13,Fwho attended Club Chemistry.
OL,15,FThe rollout of a meningitis B vaccine
OL,16,Fto about 5,000 students living on
OL,17,Fcampus in Canterbury has also begun.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
