OL,3,C'I couldn't talk, I couldn't move':
OL,4,CMeningitis patient speaks to ITV News
OL,6,FSymptoms of meningitis can include
OL,7,Ffever, seizures, vomiting, headache, a
OL,8,Fstiff neck, or a rash that does not
OL,9,Ffade when a glass is pressed against
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FSome people may also become drowsy,
OL,13,Funresponsive, or sensitive to bright
OL,14,Flights.
OL,16,FSymptoms can appear in any order and
OL,17,Fmay not always be present at once.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
